{"by":"JimmaDaRustla","id":47778764,"parent":47775628,"text":"I tried creating a whatsapp &quot;bot&quot; which would just send notifications for my Jellyfin server. It was a bureaucratic nightmare - creating dev accounts, creating some sort of &quot;project&quot;, then it was requiring I register it as a business as though the only valid use case for creating an app for WhatsApp is a business, then it required me to verify my identify and upload documents.<p>I just switched to Signal.","time":1776260093,"type":"comment"}